  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "Some caches (see [cache pkg](https://godoc.org/github.com/prysmaticlabs/prysm/beacon-chain/cache)) are causing invalid block proposals, attestations, and other unknown side effects.\r\n\r\nThis is a tracking issue to disable and carefully re-evaluate each cache mechanism.\r\n\r\nSafe caches:\r\n- [ActiveCountCache](https://github.com/prysmaticlabs/prysm/blob/e744d1a07e4ee33e77ef54d4cd84d619fc746853/beacon-chain/cache/active_count.go). The validator active count is only updated on finality. There is no risk of fork conditions to corrupt this cache.\r\n- [ActiveIndicesCache](https://github.com/prysmaticlabs/prysm/blob/e744d1a07e4ee33e77ef54d4cd84d619fc746853/beacon-chain/cache/active_indices.go). Also only updated on finality. No risk from fork condition.\r\n- [ShuffledIndicesCache](https://github.com/prysmaticlabs/prysm/blob/e744d1a07e4ee33e77ef54d4cd84d619fc746853/beacon-chain/cache/shuffled_indices.go). Indices only updated on finality. No risk from fork condition.\r\n\r\nEverything else is unsafe from forking and other conditions.\r\n- [ ] [ActiveBalanceCache](https://github.com/prysmaticlabs/prysm/blob/e744d1a07e4ee33e77ef54d4cd84d619fc746853/beacon-chain/cache/active_balance.go)\r\n- [ ] [AttestationCache](https://github.com/prysmaticlabs/prysm/blob/e744d1a07e4ee33e77ef54d4cd84d619fc746853/beacon-chain/cache/attestation_data.go)\r\n- [ ] [AncestorBlockCache](https://github.com/prysmaticlabs/prysm/blob/e744d1a07e4ee33e77ef54d4cd84d619fc746853/beacon-chain/cache/block.go)\r\n- [ ] [Eth1DataVoteCache](https://github.com/prysmaticlabs/prysm/blob/88b715d8f65a6e2bd752b02eadb30bf0b5d22f18/beacon-chain/cache/eth1_data.go)\r\n- [ ] [SeedCache](https://github.com/prysmaticlabs/prysm/blob/88b715d8f65a6e2bd752b02eadb30bf0b5d22f18/beacon-chain/cache/seed.go)\r\n- [ ] [StartShardCache](https://github.com/prysmaticlabs/prysm/blob/88b715d8f65a6e2bd752b02eadb30bf0b5d22f18/beacon-chain/cache/start_shard.go)\r\n- [ ] [TotalBalanceCache](https://github.com/prysmaticlabs/prysm/blob/e744d1a07e4ee33e77ef54d4cd84d619fc746853/beacon-chain/cache/total_balance.go)\r\n\r\nThe above caches are checked when they have been reimplemented with careful consideration or removed entirely. \r\n\r\nMisc tasks:\r\n\r\n- [x] Disable all unsafe caches and toggle via feature flags. #3107",
